	<Title>
		Slow metabolism: Is it to blame for weight gain?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Slow metabolism &amp;mdash; Are you doomed to gain weight or is something else going on?
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is it possible to be overweight because of a slow metabolism?
	</Question>
